*hermes-1.3.2-r2 (14 Apr 2002)

  14 Apr 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> all files

  This selection was moved to media-libs from app-games, since it is not
  a game, but a game/graphics library for use by games.  Artem from
  the previous ChangeLog entry brought this to my attention.

*hermes-1.3.2-r2 (14 Apr 2002)

  14 Apr 2002; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> hermes-1.3.2-r2.ebuild

  New revision to fix autogen errors.  The fix was submitted in bug #1720
  by artm@nerve.v2.nl (Artem Baguinski)

*hermes-1.3.2 (24 Feb 2002)

  25  Feb 2002; Grant Goodyear <gbevin@gentoo.org> :

  New revision to fix errors.  Thansk to Seemant Kulleen
  
  24  Feb 2002; Grant Goodyear <gbevin@gentoo.org> :

  New version needed for new clanlib ebuild.
  
*hermes-1.3.010512 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  
  Added initial ChangeLog which should be updated whenever the package is
  updated in any way. This changelog is targetted to users. This means that the
  comments should well explained and written in clean English. The details about
  writing correct changelogs are explained in the skel.ChangeLog file which you
  can find in the root directory of the portage repository.
